 / Applied.2bisacsh1 aLachowska, Anna, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015z978311067250340uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030021642440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300216424423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300216424/original  a978-3-11-067250-3  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015c2014d2015  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles